comps.description: Charming Bungalow In the Heart of Sellwood! Large covered porch welcomes you to this 3-bed 2-bath Featuring oak hardwood flooring,gas fireplace flanked by built-ins.Updated kitchen w/sweet eat area & access to private deck & Hot Tub.Master bed w/adj bath. Lower level offers separate entrance,bath, 3rd bedroom( no legal egress) living area,shop/laundry/storage. Det.garage + carport,sweet yard.Energy Score 8 out of 10!!

Easy living in this comfortable, spacious, tasteful home. Open floor plan. Perfect for entertaining! Upstairs 3BR/2BA  incl. luxurious master suite w/2 walk-in closets & gas fp. 4th BR potential in fin. bsment w/egress window & BA.  1BR/1BA in fully permitted ADU above OS 2 car garage. Great rental or guest qrters. Charming bkyard w/ raised beds & patio. Perfectly located in Sellwood, near cafes, restaurants & shops.

Best of old & new in this restored & updated Craftsman in coveted Sellwood. Integrity, charm preserved w/beautifully updated baths, kitchen, et.al. respecting the rich architecture of a true Craftsman. Huge master suite. Unique grounds alone worth the trip: new 2-car garage w/studio/ADU potential above, 2 covered porches, fenced, mature plantings, artificial turf backyard and "Drivable Grass" driveway. Brand new AC in 2018, [Home Energy Score = 4. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10079267]

Completely renovated modern oasis in the heart of Westmoreland! This exceptional home will wow you. All new features such as hardwoods, windows, paint in/out, ductless heat pump, gorgeous kitchen w/ quartz & stainless, just to name a few. Wood-burning FP, spacious BRs & light-filled dining w/ a slider outside where you'll find new easy-maintenance landscaping, an awesome new shedspace & SE PDX at your fingertips. Unbeatable location!

This Sellwood Craftsman is a testament to quality construction and period details. Well maintained and updated throughout. Including a recently remodeled Kitchen with Shaker cabinets and Stainless appliances. The upstairs was a "down to the studs" remodel with new windows, new floors, insulation, and electrical and plumbing updates. Additional updates include New paint inside/out, a tankless hot water heater and a high eff. furnace.

Delightful Sellwood bungalow with charm galore! Wonderful period details throughout including built-ins, wainscoting & hardwoods. Upper bath has clawfoot tub, skylights & laundry. Open kitchen w/sunny dining nook & tall ceilings. Living room w/gas fireplace & pocket doors that open to den, library/craft area & additional bath. Lots of potential in basement w/ office & shop area. Wonderful corner lot location close to Sellwood shops! [Home Energy Score = 1. HES Report at https://rpt.greenbuildingregistry.com/hes/OR10077246]
